      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine condition, offering an uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical profile that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every detail has been meticulously scrutinized to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. Experience the pinnacle of pre-owned luxury with this peerless acquisition.",
