      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece in truly pristine condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained, spending its life in a climate-controlled garage and receiving professional detailing monthly. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a high-grade ceramic coating, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and unmarked, still carrying that new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at certified dealerships. With exceptionally low mileage and zero modifications, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
