    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1997 Acura NSX-T is a masterclass in mid-engine balance and mechanical refinement. Powered by the high-revving 3.2L C32B V6, it features factory-spec VTEC engagement and titanium connecting rods that remain within original tolerances. The 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired perfectly with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The all-aluminum monocoque chassis is structurally flawless, supported by a precision-tuned double-wishbone suspension and four-channel ABS. Every component, from the vacuum-actuated induction system to the pristine underbody aero, reflects a vehicle kept in an uncompromising state of preservation. It is a mechanically pure example of the New Sportscar eXperimental.",
